        "description": "API方法实现：analysis.ts新增exportPdf和exportWord方法，使用Axios实例发送GET请求，responseType设为'blob'，路径：/api/analysis/{analysisId}/export/pdf 和 /api/analysis/{analysisId}/export/word",
        "priority": "P0",
        "acceptance_condition": "API方法正确发送请求并返回Blob"
      }
